# 1. What special types of observations are available in the system?

PREFIX sosa: <http://www.w3.org/ns/sosa/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX hpcc: <http://example.org/hpcc#>
PREFIX ex: <http://example.org/individuals#>
PREFIX qudt: <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/>

SELECT ?specialObservations
WHERE {
  ?specialObservations rdfs:subClassOf sosa:Observation .

}